{"tid":1804860,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［JCCAC］當藝術被政治打壓，呢幾個展幫手去睇下","createTime":"2019-12-31T09:56:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T09:40:10.000Z","uid":13388,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"b768625fd9ac680459c843ee0f54f95bd3d8fdc4","tid":1804860,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T09:56:09.000Z","msg":"收到消息<br />\n呢幾個展未開之前因為政治差d開唔成<br />\n好彩呢家開得成<br />\n但個問題係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無人支持呀！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n作為各位支持運動既手足<br />\n比個面去下睇下啦<br />\n<br />\n【#JCCAC藝術節2019】2019 香港警察系列<br />\n政府如鴕鳥一樣逃避人民的訴求，更把香港警察變成只是維護國家安全的機器，試圖造成一個太平盛世的平衡時空。<br />\n<br />\n【#JCCACFestival2019】Hong Kong Police Series 2019<br />\nLike an ostrich, the government buried its head in the sand in the face of the people&rsquo;s demands, while turning the police into a machine to enforce national security, in an attempt to establish a parallel universe of peace.<br />\n<br />\n日期 Date︰30 / 11 / 2019 &ndash; 5 / 1 / 2020<br />\n時間 Time︰10:00 &ndash; 22:00<br />\n地點 Venue︰L8 藍牆 Blue Wall<br />\n參與藝術家／藝團 Participating artist / organisation︰L8-07 海潮藝術工作室 Hoichiu Production<br />\n詳情 Details︰<a href=\"https://www.jccac.org.hk/?a=doc&amp;id=7681\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jccac.org.hk%2F%3Fa%3Ddoc%26id%3D7681&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJvZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=4ee505db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.jccac.org.hk/?a=doc&amp;id=7681</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5MV5CxU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5MV5CxU.jpg&h=292157aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【#JCCAC藝術節2019】香港 6/6/2019 &ndash; 31/8/2019（畫展）<br />\n以畫記錄香港人如何走過2019年的6月6日至8月31日。「沒有暴徒，只有&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n【#JCCACFestival2019】HONG KONG 6/6/2019 &ndash; 31/8/2019 (exhibition)<br />\nThrough paintings, Hong Kongers&rsquo; struggles from 6 June to 31 August 2019 are recorded. &quot;There are no rioters, no mob, only...&quot;<br />\n<br />\n日期 Date︰30 / 11 / 2019 &ndash; 5 / 1 / 2020<br />\n時間 Time︰10:00 &ndash; 22:00<br />\n地點 Venue︰L8 藍牆 Blue Wall<br />\n參與藝術家／藝團 Participating artist / organisation︰L6-27 肥娃藝術工作室 Miss FAT studio<br />\n詳情 Details︰<a href=\"https://www.jccac.org.hk/?a=doc&amp;id=7680\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jccac.org.hk%2F%3Fa%3Ddoc%26id%3D7680&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJvZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=c1bd2ac8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.jccac.org.hk/?a=doc&amp;id=7680</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m8uBKdc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm8uBKdc.jpg&h=389fa885&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係香港 當藝術比政治打壓時<br />\n更應該要擁護呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b0948ede4efc90d4fc82901c69016f9f5d9512","tid":1804860,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T09:56:27.000Z","msg":"睇展呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd300c1a16f61cfa0010fc1b4d47320633e4125","tid":1804860,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T09:57:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">［突發！］終於有辦法制裁新屋嶺輪姦手足班人渣黑警<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1804805\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1804805</a></span></strong>"},{"pid":"90d75526dd7f3954afa3cc790dea02d1bcbae98e","tid":1804860,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T09:57:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb6c0e46157fded66f21a794be18608ad9509c27","tid":1804860,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T09:58:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d96818a884a6bdba13ce29037a7eb833d34e256e","tid":1804860,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T09:58:46.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"41be04986274e63f6c19e57ca358af805c335943","tid":1804860,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T09:59:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b94d86da9fb620550609ed742ad8f596ccaf938f","tid":1804860,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T0